msgid "Cauldron"
msgstr "Pertza"

msgid "Stores water"
msgstr "Ur-biltegia"

msgid "Cauldrons are used to store water and slowly fill up under rain."
msgstr ""
"Galdarak ura biltzeko eta poliki-poliki euripean betetzeko erabiltzen dira."

msgid "Place a water bucket into the cauldron to fill it with water. Place an empty bucket on a full cauldron to retrieve the water. Place a water bottle into the cauldron to fill the cauldron to one third with water. Place a glass bottle in a cauldron with water to retrieve one third of the water."
msgstr ""
"Jarri kubo bat ur pertzean urez betetzeko. Jarri kubo huts bat pertza bete "
"batean ura berreskuratzeko. Jarri botila bat ur saldan, pertza heren "
"bateraino urez betetzeko. Jarri kristalezko botila bat ura duen pertza "
"batean, uraren heren bat berreskuratzeko."

msgid "Cauldron (@1/3 Water)"
msgstr "Pertza (@1/3 Ura)"

msgid "Cauldron (@1/3 Lava)"
msgstr "Pertza (@1/3 Laba)"

msgid "Cauldron (@1/3 Powder Snow)"
msgstr "Pertza (@1/3 Elur hautsa)"

msgid "Cauldron (@1/3 River Water)"
msgstr "Pertza (@1/3 Ibaiko ura)"
